about.description: A simple Modbus/TCP client library for Python
about.summary: A simple Modbus/TCP client library for Python

name: pymodbustcp
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyModbusTCP" %}
{% set version = "0.1.8" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/sourceperl/{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 9a23fdf68628dfa4e3f2156cb0996b255b2a3dced6b9fbcf21c4bb1870b72417

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  build:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  source_files:
    - tests/test_*.py

about:
  home: http://github.com/sourceperl/pyModbusTCP
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A simple Modbus/TCP client library for Python'
  description: |
    A simple Modbus/TCP client library for Python
  doc_url: http://pymodbustcp.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/sourceperl/pyModbusTCP

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - awacha
